Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.95,0:01:30.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I see... This thing does look like Eden's mascot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:32.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(224,93)}Help
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:32.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(247,210)}Board for the Lovelorn: AMORE PADRONE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:37.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.\NOsugi always had that on his bag.
