Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:54.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs36\pos(252,325)}Re: "She picked me up in Dogenzaka"\NDon't worry, you've got no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:55.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,is the same place Kasuga left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:59.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's true we have enough\Nreasons to believe it's Osugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:06.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's this "Johnny Hunter"\Nyou've been talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:09.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,She's an urban legend that's\Nbeen the talk of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:14.36,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A beautiful woman lures\Ninnocent virgins like us into hotels,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:20.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and if we can't get it up, she cuts off\Nour johnnys with a sharp instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:24.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,They say she's actually\Nclaimed 20,000 victims so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:26.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,20,000?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:30.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Naw, are you sure they're not just\Nconfusing it with those 20,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.55,0:02:36.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(333,380)}Episode 7:\NFlight of the Black Swan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:40.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But why would he ask for\Nhelp on a message board?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:46.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If it's really Osugi, he could've\Njust called or texted us directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:53.10,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This is a message board for the\Nlovelorn that Osugi frequents.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:57.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(308,96)}Board for the Lovelorn: AMORE PADRONE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:57.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(226,181)}Help
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:57.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He's been very emotionally\Nvulnerable for some time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:02.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think last night a cold wind\Nassaulted his already weak heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:05.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and he ended up going off\Nwith a sketchy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:11.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No way would his embarrassment\Nand guilt let him contact us directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.05,0:03:14.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can understand how he feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So, who is this Osugi guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:28.57,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He was so drunk! If only I'd taken\Nhim home after dinner last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:32.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,...this wouldn't have happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:35.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,By "dinner," do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:39.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes! The dinner he was supposed to eat with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:50.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A new image has been uploaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:56.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs18\pos(349,63)}Board for the lovelorn: AMORE PADRONE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:57.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It looks like he took a picture\Nof his reflection in the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:59.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Is that Osugi's suit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's definitely him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, look here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.81,0:04:08.14,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Try putting it through\NEden's image search engine!
