Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,japan purchased a few during the bubble."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we know the maker, we can\Nfigure out who bought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:32.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's our Eden System for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:34.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,There's a new comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:38.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"Her accomplice's name is Juiz"...\NWhat does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:41.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(329,210)\fn\fs36}Her accomplice's name is Juiz
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:43.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"Juiz"... For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:48.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Takky?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:52.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I've got a hunch I know where he is,\Nso I'm going to take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:02.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to find a "Stanway\NLuis 15 Model M1150" piano
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:06.57,Font 1,,0,0,0,,whose legs have been repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:08.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Accepted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:17.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's in room 1109 of the members-only\NHotel Insomnia in Roppongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:20.78,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who's staying in that room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A woman named Hanako Roppongi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,has been staying there since the year before last.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:29.19,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That sounds like an alias.\NFind out her real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Say, Juiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Do you know about the "johnny Hunter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:45.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No. Would you like me to investigate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No... That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:56.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I've finished. Her real name\Nis Diana Kuroha Shiratori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:06:00.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,She's the CEO of Monolom, an agency\Nfor foreign models in Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:03.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Where is she right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:05.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Location confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:08.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,She's in a car traveling near\NRoppongi Intersection in Minato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:11.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Isn't that near the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:14.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Juiz, stop that woman for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,How would you like me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:20.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Anything's fine. The police, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Accepted. Noblesse oblige.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:28.58,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I pray you'll be a savior of integrity,\Neven after abusing state power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What is it? I don't think I was going too fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:17.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,May I see your license, please?
