Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.65,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:46.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But what an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:49.43,Font 1,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:56.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--Stop!\N--Juiz, find me the motorbike
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:08:00.36,Font 1,,0,0,0,,that entered the Metro through\NKasumigaseki about fifteen minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.68,0:08:12.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(314,353)}Saki Morimi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hello, Takizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:17.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki! I've basically figured out where Osugi is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:18.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:21.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa says he's found Osugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:23.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:29.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think he's in room 1109 of\NHotel Insomnia in Roppongi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm about to try to go get him. Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:34.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um, Takizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.31,0:08:39.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Thank you. But how did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:57.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa? What's wrong? Takizawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:08.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(385,58)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:08.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(334,201)}[Cause a tanker truck accident\Non the Metro Expy.]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:08.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(281,314)}[Find the motorbike that entered\Nthe Metro Expy. from\NKasumigaseki 15 minutes ago]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:06.11,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:08.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hello? Takizawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:42.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So he said Osugi was at Hotel Insomnia, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I got the hotel on the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:49.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but things are crazy there and I\Ncan't get them to put me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:55.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(272,151)}WORLD VIEW NEWS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:55.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(456,271)}Tanker Overturns\Non the Metro Expressway
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:55.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's between us and Roppongi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:02.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Let's see you get into the hotel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If that's how you want to play it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.74,0:10:10.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,...I won't pull punches either!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:29.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Ah, Miss Roppongi. I'm sorry, but the\Nhotel has just changed ownership,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and no one is currently allowed in the rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:37.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So, I'm terribly sorry, but I\Nneed you to vacate your room...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But your companion isn't answering the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:46.57,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And I wasn't sure whether it would\Nbe all right for me to enter, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:48.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,That's no good, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:54.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(267,77)}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:54.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(306,213)}[Purchase Hotel Insomnia]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:54.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(369,326)}[Hotel Insomnia purchase and\Nmanagement instructions]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:54.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Number 9 bought this place for 1.5 billion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:04.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Honestly, what unnecessary expenditure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.46,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(327,178)}[Purchase Roppongi's\Nmembers-only Hotel Insomnia]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:08.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Where does the 200 million-yen difference go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(329,148)}[Purchase Roppongi's\Nmembers-only Hotel Insomnia]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:07.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(230,388)}[Cause a tanker truck\Naccedent on the Metro Expy.]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:25.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're quite ill-behaved, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Time is running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It opened, Juiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:11:59.75,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Though it took a feat of strength in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:04.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Noblesse oblige. What a violent savior you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:07.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But I pray you'll be as frugal as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear that advice right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:17.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So you're the Johnny Hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:20.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You really are a Selecao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And you're totally hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You sure don't look like a murderer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:28.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,who'd blow up tanker trucks\Nor chop off people's johnnys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:32.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Number 9, you're younger than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:37.45,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You don't look like the man\Nbehind Careless Monday, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.45,0:12:41.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, am I involved\Nin the missile crisis, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:56.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's no good. Everything's\Njammed down here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Looks like a pretty big accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:00.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Takky's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:14.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who knows? But I have\Nbeen wanting to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:17.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Though it's a shame you turned\Nout to be the Supporter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:22.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm not the Supporter. I am a Selecao, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:25.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Plus, I just came to save this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:28.40,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He's a friend of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:32.54,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A friend? Of this low life scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:36.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, from my understanding,\Nhe's not really a lowlife...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Right, Osugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:45.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Stop--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:53.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Even assuming this man is your friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:56.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can't just give him back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:03.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm a johnny-chopping killer\Nbecause of personal convictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:07.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I started long before I got this phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:12.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So I won't let anyone interfere,\Neven the Supporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:14.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm not the Supporter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:18.39,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wait, you got a Noblesse phone\Neven though you were a killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:23.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes. Though all I do with it is have\NJuiz help me find the maggots
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:26.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and dispose of their bodies afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:35.57,Font 1,,0,0,0,,"Have Juiz dispose of their bodies"?\NWhat are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:39.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What is it, Saki?\NDid you get through to Takizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:45.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:46.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:48.77,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Morimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:54.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I guess there are all kinds of Selecao.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're worlds apart from Mr. Hiura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:15:00.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But do you really think you\Ncan win the game that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:07.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,For every enemy of women that I kill,\NI import a fabulous foreign man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:12.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But I never intended to win\Nthis game in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:19.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,In the end, no champion of justice can\Nget more than half the world on her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:24.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So until I use up my ten billion, I mean\Nto carry out my own form of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:35.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Then I guess I have to take you\Ndown if I want to get Osugi back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:38.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:41.64,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Your name is Kuroha, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:45.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,How did you come up with the idea\Nof chopping off johnnys to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:51.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Do you hate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Guess I've got no choice... I'll save you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:03.22,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Because unlike you, I want to win this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:06.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,There's seriously something\Nwrong with this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.73,0:16:12.32,Font 1,,0,0,0,,This Mr. Outside even lets killers in...\NI'm gonna punch him out for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:17.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Kuroha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:20.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Did a man do something awful to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:31.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I get the feeling you've never\Ngotten love from a johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:45.09,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa, who are you talking to?\NWhat's a Selecao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:10.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder whether a johnny that\Ncould give me love even exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:13.25,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If it does, I'd love to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:45.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa! Hey, Takizawa, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:30.57,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:32.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:42.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who are you? This boy's girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:46.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What did you do to Takizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:54.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:57.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, now, looks like you've got a nice girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:03.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You'd better cherish this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:08.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Juiz? Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Wait! That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:57.93,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. He's not your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:00.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He's a wanted serial rapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:04.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,His life has no value.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:07.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder what gave that boy the wrong idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:15.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Selecao Number 9.\NLet's meet again one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.71,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:50.44,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Takizawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:56.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.18,0:20:59.21,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it, Takizawa!
