Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:12.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336,218)}[Grand illusion material rental\Nfee (including costume) for\Nthree varieties]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:12.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(314,314)}[Purchase Roppongi's\Nmembers-only Hotel Insomnia]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night is a seal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:22.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we mix in some bewilderment, it will end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:34.85,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If we're in danger of wavering,\Nlet's just abandon our reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.09,0:21:42.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We drown in dreams again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:46.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The future stretches on uncertainly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:58.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can still forgive you,\NI can still know the meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.05,0:22:02.92,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The night exists to be listened to closely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:09.06,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can copy that reason, and change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:19.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off\Nthe future to know your breath
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:25.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind cutting off the future